Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:01.68,White,,0,0,0,,(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:09.12,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:17.36,White,,0,0,0,,(cop fort: so metàl·lic)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.48,White,,0,0,0,,(cop fort)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:31.40,Green,,0,0,0,,Policia Metropolitana de Tòquio.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:33.60,Green,,0,0,0,,Iwao Takatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:36.68,Green,,0,0,0,,Queda detingut\Nper haver atracat una joieria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:40.40,White,,0,0,0,,Quina gent més mal educada. Com gosen interrompre'm a l'hora del cafè?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:45.84,White,,0,0,0,,-On ha amagat les joies que va robar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:45.84,White,,0,0,0,,-On és el seu còmplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ho sento, però no sé\Nde què em parlen, la veritat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:52.32,Green,,0,0,0,,No dissimuli.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:54.68,Green,,0,0,0,,Sabem que ahir,\Ncap a les 8 del vespre,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.80,Green,,0,0,0,,va entrar en una joieria de Beika
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.28,Green,,0,0,0,,i va robar joies i pedres precioses valorades en 300 milions de iens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.36,White,,0,0,0,,-(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:10.08,White,,0,0,0,,(Takagi) El seu còmplice és\Nen Tokuro Utsumi, de 32 anys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.48,White,,0,0,0,,I no és la primera vegada que participen junts en un atracament.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:20.28,White,,0,0,0,,En Tokuro, diu? Aquell tio\Nés un idiota, ja no és el meu soci.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.72,Green,,0,0,0,,Com?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:24.36,White,,0,0,0,,Per cert,\Ncom ho saben, que vaig ser jo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:27.12,White,,0,0,0,,M'han vist bé la cara\Nen alguna càmera de seguretat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:29.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:29.68,Green,,0,0,0,,Doncs, de fet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:33.04,White,,0,0,0,,Llavors,\Nem penso que ja hem acabat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:36.76,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Kogoro) No.\NAixò tot just acaba de començar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:42.44,White,,0,0,0,,És... el Kogoro Dorment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.68,White,,0,0,0,,Armats amb pistoles,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:47.16,White,,0,0,0,,van entrar a la joieria\Ni van robar unes pedres precioses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.44,White,,0,0,0,,que havien arribat just abans\Nque tanqués la botiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:53.28,White,,0,0,0,,Tots sabem que és la seva especialitat, senyor Takatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.44,White,,0,0,0,,I encara hi ha una altra cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.60,White,,0,0,0,,Tot i que van fer servir màscares,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.40,White,,0,0,0,,les càmeres de seguretat\Nvan gravar una prova irrefutable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.12,Green,,0,0,0,,Ho tens ben clar, tot això, Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:05.04,White,,0,0,0,,Naturalment, inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.28,White,,0,0,0,,La prova és... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.24,White,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Alerta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Correu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.44,White,,0,0,0,,(estossega)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.08,Green,,0,0,0,,A la porta lateral!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:28.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.20,White,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:38.80,Green,,0,0,0,,No es mogui.\NSenyor Takatori, no faci ni un pas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:42.00,White,,0,0,0,,Ma... marrec.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:42.00,Green,,0,0,0,,Eh? És en Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:45.08,White,,0,0,0,,Q-què hi fas, aquí? Però d'on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:45.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,He-he!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.00,White,,0,0,0,,-A-aquí corres perill, ves-te'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:50.08,White,,0,0,0,,-(carrega l'arma)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:50.08,White,,0,0,0,,-(Takatori) Aixeca't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:55.84,White,,0,0,0,,Val més que no es mogui ningú.\NO li rebentaré el cap a aquest nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.48,White,,0,0,0,,L'hi esclafaré\Ncom si fos un tomàquet madur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.84,White,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.72,White,,0,0,0,,(rodes: xerriquen)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.28,White,,0,0,0,,-(Takagi) S'escapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.28,White,,0,0,0,,-(Kogoro) Alto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.76,White,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.60,Green,,0,0,0,,Dispositiu de recerca.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.60,White,,0,0,0,,Oh, merda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.52,Green,,0,0,0,,De pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Quan el compte enrere\Narriba a zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:20.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,la deducció és l'única resposta."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"M'han segrestat\Nmentre resolia un cas."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Això sí que no m'havia passat mai."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:30.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:37.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,Honno suubyou de fukitobu mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:51.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Soshite semarareta\Nniritsu no se wo osu aa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:55.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Karamitsuita kono koodo\Nwo kiru kurai de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Konna namakura ga omotai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:03.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,furuete shimau shimatsu da.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kagen shirazu no sujigaki de
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,saishuukai temae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:14.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ima byouyomi no owari ga temaneku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:19.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi no inai mirai nante\Nerabitaku mo nai yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:25.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ichibyou saki no boku\Nyo kotae wo dashite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:33.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kagen shirazu no sujigaki de
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,saishuukai temae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:42.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ima byouyomi no owari ga temaneku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:47.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi no inai mirai nante\Nerabitaku mo nai yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:54.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ichibyou saki no boku\Nyo kotae wo dashite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:04.64,Songs2,,0,0,0,,"El segrest d'en Conan.\NPrimera part."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:11.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.72,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) Ja ho entenc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:17.52,White,,0,0,0,,Mentre jo dormia... vull dir, mentre exposava la meva teoria sobre el cas,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.40,White,,0,0,0,,tot s'ha torçat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.28,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector, ja sé que...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.12,White,,0,0,0,,la meva reputació ha quedat molt tocada després d'aquest incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.92,White,,0,0,0,,però ara la nostra prioritat\Nha de ser rescatar el nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.80,Green,,0,0,0,,Ja ho sé, home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.08,Green,,0,0,0,,Hem col·locat punts de control\Na totes les carreteres
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:33.48,Green,,0,0,0,,i, a més,\Ntornarem a investigar l'atracament.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:44.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(pensa: veu Shinichi) "Què\Ndeu haver vist?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un punt de control.\NQuè pensa fer, ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sembla que té decidit on vol anar\Ni per on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:59.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,però si continua per aquest carrer,\Nl'enxamparan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Així doncs,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.64,Green,,0,0,0,,les pedres que van robar són només les que havien arribat a la botiga
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.76,Green,,0,0,0,,just abans de l'hora\Nde tancament, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:14.56,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, ho vaig comprovar de seguida\Nper assegurar-me'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:18.04,White,,0,0,0,,Només van robar les més cares, valorades en uns 5 milions cadascuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.64,White,,0,0,0,,És un bon daltabaix per nosaltres.\NNo sé què farem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:26.20,White,,0,0,0,,L'hora d'entrega de la comanda\Ndevia ser confidencial, suposo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.04,White,,0,0,0,,Esclar que sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:32.04,White,,0,0,0,,No ho sabia ningú, ni tan sols\Nel personal de la botiga. Oi que no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.48,White,,0,0,0,,No. Per això no ens en sabem avenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.60,White,,0,0,0,,Jo tampoc entenc\Ncom es va filtrar la informació.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.88,White,,0,0,0,,Tot i així, el proveïdor de les joies i l'empresa de transports...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.92,White,,0,0,0,,bé que en devien estar al cas,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.52,White,,0,0,0,,i són col·laboradors externs\Nque vostè no controla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.56,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, naturalment.\NSuposo que té raó, esclar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:52.08,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector.\NEn sabem res, d'en Takagi i en Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Encara no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.16,Green,,0,0,0,,I els punts de control d'emergència\Nque hem instal·lat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.92,Green,,0,0,0,,tampoc han localitzat el cotxe\Nque busquem, pel que sembla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.92,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs l'únic que tenim de moment\Nés aquesta línia d'investigació.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.92,White,,0,0,0,,Hem de trobar una pista
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:07.84,White,,0,0,0,,que ens ajudi a descobrir on paren l'Iwao Takatori i el marrec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.80,Green,,0,0,0,,Sí. Bé, doncs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:13.20,Green,,0,0,0,,Faré que investiguin el proveïdor de les joies i l'empresa de transports.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.72,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, sisplau.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Que curiós.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ara que m'hi fixo,\Naquest cotxe no porta navegador.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Miri, ara som\Nal carrer Kitahinode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Si agafem el trencall\Nque acabem de passar
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,anirem a parar al carrer Nakahotoke,\Nque és paral·lel a aquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Vaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.36,White,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:39.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És que m'agrada molt que em portin\Na passejar amb cotxe per la ciutat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i tinc memòria pels carrers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Allà podrem anar de compres,\Nsi vol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,L'escala de corda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.12,White,,0,0,0,,Com?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:50.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No sé per què la volia fer servir,\Nperò l'hi ha caigut mentre fugia."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,En un carrer principal, potser hi trobarem una botiga de bricolatge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ets tot un personatge, noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,He-he...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:04.68,White,,0,0,0,,(rodes: xerriquen)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:14.72,White,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Què passa? Per què no hi ha ningú?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ni un telèfon públic."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Les botigues...\Nestan totes tancades?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja m'ha trobat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:59.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja ve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,M'atropellarà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Uf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.60,White,,0,0,0,,Anem-nos-en.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:44.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Daixò... no m'he pogut fixar bé\Nen aquella capsa de llumins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja no me'n recordo com era.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Li prometo que no explicaré res\Nde vostè a la policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:51.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No ho ha pensat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Si em porta a tot arreu, cridarà\Nl'atenció i el trobaran de seguida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I, si em permet que l'hi digui,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:00.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,no fa cara de ser el meu pare\Nni el meu germà gran, la veritat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:07.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,em sembla que el que sí que hauríem de fer és canviar de cotxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:10.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I, a més, podríem intercanviar la matrícula per la d'un altre vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:13.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Segur que hi té la mà trencada,\Na fer aquestes coses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:16.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aaaai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:20.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aniria tan bé que poguéssim escoltar\Nla ràdio de la policia des d'aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Així podríem saber\Nquè han descobert,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:25.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,ens anticiparíem\Na tots els seus plans
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:27.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i sabríem\Non són els punts de control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.00,White,,0,0,0,,(carrega l'arma)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.52,White,,0,0,0,,(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Daixò... no m'he pogut fixar bé\Nen aquella capsa de llumins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja no me'n recordo com era.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:48.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Li prometo que no explicaré res\Nde vostè a la policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No ho ha pensat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:54.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Si em porta a tot arreu, cridarà\Nl'atenció i el trobaran de seguida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I, si em permet que l'hi digui,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:59.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,no fa cara de ser el meu pare\Nni el meu germà gran, la veritat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,em sembla que el que sí que hauríem de fer és canviar de cotxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:09.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I, a més, podríem intercanviar la matrícula per la d'un altre vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Segur que hi té la mà trencada,\Na fer aquestes coses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aaaai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:19.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aniria tan bé que poguéssim escoltar\Nla ràdio de la policia des d'aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Així podríem saber\Nquè han descobert,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,ens anticiparíem\Na tots els seus plans
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i sabríem\Non són els punts de control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.68,White,,0,0,0,,(carrega l'arma)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.16,White,,0,0,0,,(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:36.88,White,,0,0,0,,No t'ho repetiré.\NNo et vull sentir més.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,E-entesos...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.88,White,,0,0,0,,Si creus que cridem massa l'atenció,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.76,White,,0,0,0,,et puc portar lligat al maleter\Nfins que arribem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"A on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:53.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Per què no em deixa anar, si sap\Nque li faré més nosa que servei?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.64,White,,0,0,0,,(trepant)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.32,White,,0,0,0,,(trepant)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:22.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ara mateix no porta a sobre totes les pedres precioses que va robar."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:27.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Per tant, és molt probable que vulgui anar a veure el seu còmplice,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que deu tenir el que falta\Ndel botí; tot i que abans..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:34.76,White,,0,0,0,,En Tokuro, diu? Aquell tio\Nés un idiota, ja no és el meu soci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Què devia passar entre tots dos?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Oh! "Allò és..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.96,White,,0,0,0,,Queda clar? Si fuges, disparo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:01.28,White,,0,0,0,,Si no vols morir aquí i acabar esquarterat pels gossos salvatges,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.48,White,,0,0,0,,fes el que et digui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:07.60,White,,0,0,0,,Si fas bondat, és probable que no em faci falta una escala de corda nova.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí, ho he entès.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.60,White,,0,0,0,,Ho has entès?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.32,White,,0,0,0,,Continua.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.12,White,,0,0,0,,Atura't aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aquí?\NA l'entrada d'aquesta xemeneia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.96,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, aquí mateix.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:29.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Esclar. Per això necessitava\Nl'escala de corda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.56,White,,0,0,0,,La volia per baixar fins a dins\Nde la xemeneia des de dalt,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:36.52,White,,0,0,0,,però ara ja no farà falta,\Nperquè hi entraràs tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Vol que em fiqui aquí dins?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:46.68,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure. Hem trobat el cotxe que ha robat l'Iwao Takatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.60,White,,0,0,0,,Aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.60,Green,,0,0,0,,On era?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.84,White,,0,0,0,,Uns agents l'han trobat abandonat\Na l'aparcament subterrani
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:54.16,White,,0,0,0,,d'un centre comercial\Ndel carrer Nakahotoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.08,White,,0,0,0,,No en sabem res, del nen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:14:00.16,White,,0,0,0,,De moment no hem trobat a ningú\Nque hagi vist en Conan ni l'Iwao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:01.84,White,,0,0,0,,Continuen desapareguts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.88,Green,,0,0,0,,Hmm...\NI han sortit de l'aparcament a peu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:07.20,Green,,0,0,0,,No, esclar.\NDeuen haver canviat de cotxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.92,White,,0,0,0,,Exactament.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ara només ens falta saber\Nen quina direcció han marxat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:17.88,White,,0,0,0,,Estic convençut que ha anat a buscar el seu còmplice i les pedres robades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.76,Green,,0,0,0,,En aquest cas, doncs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.24,Green,,0,0,0,,no tenim més remei\Nque ampliar la zona de recerca.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:24.16,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:24.16,Green,,0,0,0,,Takagi, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.60,White,,0,0,0,,(telèfon)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.36,Green,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure, digui'm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.60,Green,,0,0,0,,Com? Què has dit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.20,Green,,0,0,0,,I es pot saber què vol dir això?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.56,Green,,0,0,0,,Entesos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.44,Green,,0,0,0,,Sí, gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:47.48,Green,,0,0,0,,Una trucada de la comissaria local.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:47.48,White,,0,0,0,,Hi ha novetats, inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:49.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Es veu que el cap de compres\Nde la joieria,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:53.12,Green,,0,0,0,,el senyor Yamaga,\Nha desaparegut sense deixar rastre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.44,White,,0,0,0,,Què diu, ara!? Llavors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.80,Green,,0,0,0,,Exacte.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:59.68,Green,,0,0,0,,S'ha esfumat tan aviat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:01.96,Green,,0,0,0,,com hem començat a investigar\Nel seu proveïdor i el transportista.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.28,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.68,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.68,Green,,0,0,0,,Tornem a la joieria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Punyeta.\NSe'm deu haver trencat quan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Vaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això no m'ho esperava,\Nés un bon entrebanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.92,White,,0,0,0,,(Takatori) Em sents, nano?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:28.32,White,,0,0,0,,Vull que tornis\Nd'aquí 3 minuts justos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.56,White,,0,0,0,,Si arribes un segon més tard,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.68,White,,0,0,0,,ficaré això dins la xemeneia\Ndarrere teu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Eh?\NHo deu dir de broma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:38.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Si encén el paper em quedaré atrapat entre el fum i moriré asfixiat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.48,White,,0,0,0,,T'ha quedat clar, noi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) M'ha quedat clar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Ostres.\NNo s'acaba mai, això.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:50.04,White,,0,0,0,,(Shimazu) No ho entenc.\NQuè vol dir tot això?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.96,Green,,0,0,0,,És precisament\Nel que estem investigant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.20,White,,0,0,0,,Em permet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.52,White,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Això confirma les sospites.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.60,White,,0,0,0,,-(Shimazu) Però si són...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:07.24,White,,0,0,0,,Lla-llavors, ha sigut en Yamaga...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.40,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, això deu ser la seva recompensa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.84,White,,0,0,0,,per haver filtrat\Ninformació als lladres.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.36,White,,0,0,0,,No pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:17.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Ell sabia que, quan interroguéssim\Nel proveïdor i el transportista,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.08,Green,,0,0,0,,tard o d'hora descobriríem\Nque ell era la persona
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:23.12,Green,,0,0,0,,que havia informat els lladres\Nde l'horari d'entrega de les pedres.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.64,Green,,0,0,0,,Per això s'ha estimat\Nmés desaparèixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Ostres, no m'ho puc creure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.20,White,,0,0,0,,-No n'hi ha cap dubte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.48,Green,,0,0,0,,Trobeu-lo immediatament!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:39.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Això s'acaba aquí. Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,La sortida de la xemeneia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ostres.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Qui és aquest home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:01.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ha de ser en Tokuro Utsumi,\Nel còmplice de l'atracament.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,De què ha mort?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:08.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Té contusions múltiples\Nper tot el cos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Escolti.\NQuè hi feia, ell, aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,L'ha mort vostè?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.04,White,,0,0,0,,Al contrari. Va ser ell,\Nque va intentar matar-me a mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.40,White,,0,0,0,,(Utsumi) Ho hem aconseguit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:31.56,White,,0,0,0,,Quina passada! Què,\Nanem a fer una copa per celebrar-ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.88,White,,0,0,0,,-No, encara no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:38.16,White,,0,0,0,,Li entregarem les pedres a ell,\Ntal com havíem acordat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.32,White,,0,0,0,,i ens donarà els diners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:43.76,White,,0,0,0,,Després ho podrem celebrar.\ND'aquí dues hores allà on tu ja saps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:46.24,White,,0,0,0,,Entesos, ja hi pots comptar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:49.12,White,,0,0,0,,Apa, fins després.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.60,White,,0,0,0,,És estrany\Nque encara no hagi arribat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.48,White,,0,0,0,,(clau: cau a terra)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.56,White,,0,0,0,,(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.00,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.08,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:16.20,White,,0,0,0,,(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.48,White,,0,0,0,,-(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.48,White,,0,0,0,,-(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.04,White,,0,0,0,,(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:42.60,White,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.76,White,,0,0,0,,(Takatori) Tokuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:50.88,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.96,White,,0,0,0,,Ja han passat els 3 minuts, noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:00.96,White,,0,0,0,,Torna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:02.80,White,,0,0,0,,El fum t'espavilarà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:06.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un moment.\NJa vinc, torno de seguida.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:10.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Merda, està tot ple de sutge i no hi ha cap pista.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:13.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I allà dalt no hi podré pujar\Nde cap manera.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:18.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Valdrà més...\Nque agafi les pedres i torni.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.88,White,,0,0,0,,Això és tot el que has trobat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.96,White,,0,0,0,,No et servirà de res,\Namagar les pedres.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:28.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No he amagat res, jo. De fet,\Na mi també m'ha semblat estrany.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:32.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Les pedres que han robat\Nvalen 300 milions de iens, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És evident\Nque no hi són totes, aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ha sigut ell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:41.36,White,,0,0,0,,En Tokuro es va deixar enredar\Nper la seva xerrameca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.52,White,,0,0,0,,Segur que ell el va convèncer\Nperquè em matés.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.88,White,,0,0,0,,per menys de la meitat\Ndel que havíem acordat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.32,White,,0,0,0,,Que idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ell? Qui és "ell"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:55.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir...\Nque l'han traït?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:20:01.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I ara què pensa fer?\NVoldrà venjar-se d'aquesta persona?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:13.76,White,,0,0,0,,La teva feina ja s'ha acabat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:16.64,White,,0,0,0,,Ara procura mantenir\Nla curiositat a ratlla, marrec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:20.28,White,,0,0,0,,Si et penses que no m'atreviré\Na matar-te perquè ets petit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.28,White,,0,0,0,,estàs molt equivocat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"On anem? En quina direcció?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:48.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ha reduït la velocitat. Per què?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Què pretén fer?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.20,White,,0,0,0,,(Takatori) Vols tornar a sortir\Ndel cotxe, noi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:56.24,White,,0,0,0,,Si estàs de sort,\Npotser et salvaràs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:02.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.88,White,,0,0,0,,A reveure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:11.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:20.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,("First place", Sadame)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:26.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sadamerareta you ni\Nsuki ni natte yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:31.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,anata no egao sukoshi chiisana te.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:37.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kinou yori mo kyou\Nkyou yori mo ashita
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:42.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,bokura wa kitto shiawase ni nareru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:48.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Omoi ukabete goran\Ntooi mirai no futari,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:56.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,shiwakucha ni natta te to te\Ntsunagi nagara sanpo shiteru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:22:01.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Egao wo kasanete kita hibi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:07.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,anata ga unmei no hito desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:13.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Haru natsu aki fuyu yumemite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:18.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,futari de zutto zutto ikite ikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:24.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Daiji na bokunari no yume desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:32.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Anata wo shiawase ni sasete ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.44,0:22:36.44,White,,0,0,0,,(Takagi) No n'hi ha cap dubte.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:40.36,White,,0,0,0,,El cadàver que hi ha a la xemeneia és d'en Tokuro, el còmplice de l'Iwao.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.68,White,,0,0,0,,Sisplau, torni a activar\Nel dispositiu de recerca.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:45.92,Green,,0,0,0,,Sí, ara mateix.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:48.88,White,,0,0,0,,Però t'has descuidat la meva part.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:50.92,White,,0,0,0,,I també vull una propina
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:53.24,White,,0,0,0,,per haver-li encarregat a en Tokuro\Nque em matés.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:56.16,White,,0,0,0,,Estàs massa espantat\Nper obrir la boca, o què?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:00.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No us perdeu el pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:02.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,'El segrest d'en Conan.\NSegona part'."
